This paper is about video captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) categories. The paper also proposes new techniques to improve the performance of the model, which falls under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the experiments are conducted on video datasets, indicating that the paper may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
